{"tid":176526,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被告曾指遭事主「睇唔起」","createTime":"2017-03-28T08:43:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T08:44:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7f6e661a1f26ccd94379e6182c8fa4977e08f0d1","tid":176526,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T08:43:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19972262&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170328\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19972262%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170328&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0ZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=ddd2d528\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19972262%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170328&h=1695df12\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19972262&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170328</a><br />\n<br />\n被告曾指遭事主「睇唔起」<br />\n<br />\n法庭&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n院牧劉鳳雲<br />\n<br />\n【渠蓋殺人案】<br />\n【本報訊】患老人癡呆症的八旬老翁涉在兩名長期卧床的同房男院友熟睡期間，用浴室渠蓋襲擊對方致一死一重傷，案件昨在高院續審。院舍院牧供稱被告斯文、平靜，但曾多次投訴兩名事主偷竊，又指二人對他不瞅不睬「睇佢（被告）唔起」。<br />\n在涉案將軍澳靈實胡平頤養院擔任院牧的劉鳳雲指，曾向被告周利鴻（87歲）解釋兩事主因生病及退化症問題而長期卧床，並非沒禮貌，惟被告「好似唔係好明白」。她表示自2015年起沒再聽到被告投訴。聆訊今續。<br />\n案件編號：HCCC480/16<br />\n■記者楊思雅"},{"pid":"989b8cad733c63c6fd8d9600b721a91d55905d6f","tid":176526,"uid":83941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T08:44:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}